# MadCache 0.5

# Setup
Open MadCache0.5.inc.php change your BASE_PATH to the path to your cache_files folder.

Change the cache_files folder to 777 permissions (or any permissions on your server
that the webserver can write. (NOTE: If your server (www-data, apache, nobody, etc) writes
the files, please be sure that you can delete them. Sometimes you're not able to on
a managed host.)

Setup a crontab for doing Garbage Collection
